  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV96">
<l>vaṇaṅkun tuṟaikaḷ palapala vākki mativikaṟpāṟ</l>
<l>piṇaṅkuñ camayam palapala vākki yavaiyavaitō</l>
<l>ṟaṇaṅkum palapala vākkiniṉ mūrtti parappivaittā</l>
<l>yiṇaṅkuniṉ ṉōraiyil lāyniṉkaṇ vēṭkai yeḻuvippaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Creating many many ways of worship, creating many many creeds</l>
<l>intertwined with the diversity of minds, creating many many torments</l> 
<l>with any of these, you who spread [and] put down your form,</l>
<l>you who are without match, in you I shall raise [my] desire.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
